The following scripts are explored;  Python XML DOM Minidom.  ‘xml.dom.minidom’ is a minimal DOM implementation.  xml.dom.minidom is a minimal implementation of the Document Object Model interface, with an API similar to that in other languages. It is intended to be simpler than the full DOM and also significantly smaller. Users who are not already proficient with the DOM should consider using the xml.etree.ElementTree module for their XML processing instead.  Python XHTML Parser.  ‘html.parser’ is a simple HTML and XHTML parser.
